[00:01.51]Lesson 19
[00:04.21]Tired and thirsty | 又累又渴
[00:07.55]Listen to the tape then answer this question. | 听录音，然后回答问题。
[00:13.63]Why do the children thank their mother? | 孩子们为什么感谢他们的母亲？
[00:19.10]What's the matter, children? | 怎么了，孩子们？
[00:22.74]We're tired �� | 我们累了，我们累了，我们累了
[00:25.13]�� and thirsty, Mum. | 口渴，妈妈。
[00:27.78]Sit down here. | 坐在这里。
[00:31.24]Are you all right now? | 你们现在好了吗？
[00:33.77]No, we aren't. | 不，还没好。
[00:37.46]Look! | 看！
[00:39.09]There's an ice cream man. | 有个卖冰淇淋的人。
[00:43.80]Two ice cream please. | 请来两个冰淇淋。
[00:48.33]Here you are, children. | 给你们，孩子们。
[00:51.74]Thanks, Mum. | 谢谢，妈妈。
[00:55.00]These ice creams are nice. | 这些冰淇淋很好吃。
[00:59.61]Are you all right now? | 你们现在好了吗？
[01:02.87]Yes, we are, thank you! | 是的，我们好了，谢谢你！
